# Quotation Feature Components

This rule highlights the core components involved in creating a new quotation.

## Main Entry Point

- **`[nueva-cotizacion/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/nueva-cotizacion/page.tsx)`**: The main page component for the new quotation form.

## Key Components

- **`[cliente-form.tsx](mdc:src/components/cotizacion/cliente-form.tsx)`**: Form for capturing and validating client information.
- **`[producto-simplificado.tsx](mdc:src/components/cotizacion/producto-simplificado.tsx)`**: Form used to add individual products/items to the quote.
- **`[lista-productos.tsx](mdc:src/components/cotizacion/lista-productos.tsx)`**: Table component that displays the list of added products, allowing management (e.g., removal).

## State Management

- **`[productos-context.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/productos-context.tsx)`**: Manages the state of the products added to the current quotation, likely providing functions to add, remove, and update products.
